    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nAll queries that ship with Neovim have been formatted using [nvim-treesitter's query formatter](https://github.com/nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter/blob/master/scripts/format-queries.lua) in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/f5dc45310941dff6efc02d955fc0c110190e9b85.\r\nAssuming this is the format that core approves of, it would be nice to push/help users to use this format when writing their own queries by having it as the default formatter for query files.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nTransform [nvim-treesitter's query formatter](https://github.com/nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter/blob/master/scripts/format-queries.lua) into a `formatexpr` and apply it in [`ftplugin/query.lua`](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/tree/master/runtime/ftplugin/query.lua)",
    "closed_at": "2024-01-24T10:53:12Z",
